# read_theory_cluster_demo.md

## File
utils/theory-cluster/theory_cluster_demo.py

---

## 1. Purpose

Generate realistic, audit-grade, prescriptive corporate document blueprints per procedure, based on improved theory outputs.

Reads:
utils/theory-cluster/output/improved/<DOMAIN>_theory_improved_output.json

Writes:
utils/theory-cluster/output/demo/<DOMAIN>_theory_demo_output.json

Optional:
utils/theory-cluster/output/demo/<DOMAIN>_theory_demo_output_PATCHED.json

This is the final simulation layer of the DOMMx Theory Stack.

