## 11. Execution Examples

Generate one domain:
python theory_cluster_demo.py --mode domain --domain DG

Generate all domains:
python theory_cluster_demo.py --mode all

Force regeneration:
python theory_cluster_demo.py --mode domain --domain DG --clear-cache

Apply deterministic patch:
python theory_cluster_demo.py --mode domain --domain DG --patch

